content.data: Currently, only a single CV object is exposed in the managed API. It is named CVAsmManaged. CVAsmManaged exposes properties and methods. The properties are shorthand methods for getting and setting common parameters, while methods are exposed for more complex operations.
There are a number of predefined numeric constants used for parameter types and object properties. The constants can be used in conditional checking and method calls. For example

VAL_MEASUREMENT 
 
 
 VAL_DEGREES
